graph TD
    subgraph Frontend [LostLink Client Application]
        A1[User Submits Form] --> |Photos, Description, Map Pin| B{Report Type}
        B --> |Lost Item| C1[Lost Form Context]
        B --> |Found Item| C2[Found Form Context]
    end

    subgraph API Layer [Backend Services]
        D[Express/Fastify API]
    end

    subgraph AI Processing [LLM Engine]
        E1[Vision Model] --> |Extracts features from photo| E3[Data Normalization]
        E2[Text Model] --> |Extracts entities from description| E3
        E3 --> |Outputs JSON: brand, color, category, distinguishing marks| E4[Embedding Generation]
    end

    subgraph Data Store [Database & Location]
        F1[(PostgreSQL + PostGIS)]
        F2[(Vector DB / pgvector)]
    end

    C1 --> |Payload| D
    C2 --> |Payload| D

    D --> |Images| E1
    D --> |Text| E2

    D --> |Lat/Lng Coords| F1

    E3 --> |Structured Metadata| F1
    E4 --> |Vectors| F2


    F1 <--> |Radius Filtering query: ST_DWithin| M[Match Engine]
    F2 <--> |Cosine Similarity| M

    M --> |High Confidence Match| N[Notification Service Push/Email]
    M --> |Stores Match % in DB| F1
